------------------------------------------------------*/

// Selects how the product of two n-limb integers is reduced modulo N.
// MOD_RED_MONTGOMERY: REDC — operands live in Montgomery form (x·R mod N);
//   requires a conversion step but shares the NTT buffer with the multiply.
